shocking

7
00:00:17,269 --> 00:00:20,000
and outrageous last Friday.

8
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,770
They sent a ship...

9
00:00:21,770 --> 00:00:23,769
through the ocean.

10
00:00:23,769 --> 00:00:25,970
The South China Sea, to be exact.

11
00:00:25,970 --> 00:00:27,850
Near here, the Paracel Islands.

12
00:00:27,850 --> 00:00:32,210
They’re about 200 miles from the coast of
mainland China.

13
00:00:32,210 --> 00:00:37,360
And steering a ship near there is totally
and completely legal—

14
00:00:37,360 --> 00:00:39,510
because it’s international waters.

15
00:00:39,510 --> 00:00:41,930
Unless you’re the Chinese regime,

16
00:00:41,930 --> 00:00:45,180
and the Paracel Islands are actually the Xisha
Islands,

17
00:00:45,180 --> 00:00:48,830
which have been China’s territory since
ancient times.

18
00:00:48,830 --> 00:00:51,020
Haha, oh dear.

19
00:00:51,020 --> 00:00:53,530
So I am wondering the same thing this reporter
is:

20
00:00:54,040 --> 00:00:56,340
"Are you concerned at all that China

21
00:00:56,340 --> 00:00:59,160
will view this as a provocative act?"

22
